OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with some patchy light
OL,7,Frain possible at times. Remaining
OL,8,Fmainly cloudy through the rest of the
OL,9,Fnight with a few mist or fog patches
OL,10,Fdeveloping.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FBright but with few spots of
OL,13,Flight rain not to be ruled out, though
OL,14,Fmany places staying dry until
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain spread across from
OL,16,Fthe southwest by late afternoon.
